cost_description: Free, but in a restaurant parking lot with restricted hours of being open to EV
description: Dual pedestal with one spot reserved for EV charging (except between 5 - 10 pm Thursday - Saturday). www.evolveky.org. Evolve KY location #6
hours: While it is accessible 24/7, one side of the lot by the Irish rover is only reserved for EV until 5 Thurs-Sat each day. Don’t park here outside then unless you are eating there. I have seen the owner ask people to leave (makes sense, it’s his lot). However, outside of these hours if that lot is full you can also stretch the cable over to two spots by the public lot right next to it which is unrestricted.
